Show package options

Source: R/show_options.R
show_options.Rd

See surveytable-options for a discussion of some of the options.

Usage

show_options(sw = "surveytable")

Arguments

sw

starting characters

Value

List of options and their values.

See also

Other options: set_survey(), surveytable-options

Examples

show_options()
